"Torsion Stiffness Matrix
'K = ∫ Bᵀ·G·J·B dx — same form as axial

"Shape Functions (linear)
#deq N_1 = 1 - ξ
#deq N_2 = ξ
#sym diff(1-t; t)
#sym diff(t; t)

"Stiffness Matrix
#deq K_torsion = G*J/L*[1; -1 | -1; 1]

"Numerical
G = 80000MPa
J = 5000cm^4
L = 4m
K_t = G*J/L*[1; -1 | -1; 1]
K_t|[kN*m/rad; kN*m/rad | kN*m/rad; kN*m/rad]
